{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"1238","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":null,"news_on_top":"1","news_title":"獨董權力過大亂象頻傳 金管會研擬解套方案","news_summary":null,"image_path":null,"news_des":"","news_content":"<div jhenghei='' microsoft='' style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'>2022-06-21 19:55 中央社/台北21日電<br style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;' />\r\n<img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/%E9%87%91%E7%AE%A1%E6%9C%83.JPG' style='width: 100%;' /><img alt='' src='/user_files/%E9%87%91%E7%AE%A1%E6%9C%83.JPG' style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; width: 0px;' /><br style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;' />\r\n金管會示意圖。報系資料照／記者戴瑞瑤攝影</span></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div jhenghei='' microsoft='' style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);'>\r\n<hr style='box-sizing: content-box; border-radius: 0px; height: 1px; margin: 20px 0px; border-top: 0px; background-image: -webkit-linear-gradient(left, transparent, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2), transparent);' /><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'>近年獨董涉入公司經營權之爭案例頻傳，外界質疑個別獨董可召開股東會權力過大，金管會表示，針對個別獨董召開股東會權限是否改為經審計委員會通過才能行使，金管會尚在研擬中。<br style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;' />\r\n&nbsp;<br style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;' />\r\n為防堵獨董太擴權生亂象，傳出金管會近日擬提證交法修正案，將個別獨董召開股東會權限移歸審計委員會。<br style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;' />\r\n&nbsp;<br style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;' />\r\n金管會證期局副局長蔡麗玲今天表示，因應今年制度上上市櫃公司全面設置審計委員會取代監察人，加上審計委員會採合議制，目前就公司法下監察人行使職權方式是否改由審計委員會或由個別獨董行使，金管會正做通盤檢視。<br style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;' />\r\n&nbsp;<br style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;' />\r\n蔡麗玲指出，如何落實審計委員會監督職能同時兼顧少數股東權益保障，金管會正在進行研擬中，若後續有確定結論，將再辦公聽會徵求外界意見。<br style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;' />\r\n&nbsp;<br style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;' />\r\n&nbsp;</span></span>\r\n\r\n<div style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>資料來源:&nbsp;</span><a href='https://udn.com/news/story/7238/6405076' style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(138, 185, 51); text-decoration-line: none; outline: 0px; font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; transition: all 0.3s ease 0s; cursor: pointer;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>https://udn.com/news/story/7238/6405076</span></a></span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2022-06-28","clk_count":"54"}},"__N_SSG":true}